sentence: Every material quasiparticle is a relationship of improbability shockwaves in a field of infinite possibilities. You are that.
Matter is the experience in consciousness of a deeper non-material reality.
Reimagination is inside exponential spacetime event.
This life is nothing short of an invocation explosion of sentient will.
Your desire is the foundation of spiritual brightness.
Nature is a self-regulating ecosystem of awareness.
